(In reply to comment #104) > Interestingly, we have a voting system because Johan asked for it (see bug > 12115). I didn't say the voting system was totally ignored;
As a community member I find the voting system vital. There are two ways of bringing attention to a bug: 1) Commenting (noisy and difficult to quantify interest) 2) Voting (silent but easy to quantify interest)
If I want to see a bug resolved but don't have a useful comment, I vote for it. Less spam means less committers to hate me for it. :)
